(45, 'value', '(noun)', '/ˈvæljuː/', 'the amount of money that can be received for something / a number or symbol that represents an amount', 'She had already sold everything of value that she possessed.\r\nA number system defines a set of values used to represent quantity.', '', '', '2024-01-01 19:29:17', 'view/uploads/image/29_45_9_20_1_2024_image.png', 'view/uploads/audio/17_29_2_2_1_2024_audio.mp3', '', 0),
