(118, 'practical', '(adjective)', '/ˈpræktɪkl/', 'relating to experience, real situations, or actions rather than ideas or imagination / suitable for the situation in which something is used / hữu ích / thực tế / thiết thực', 'External scripts are practical when the same code is used in many different web pages.\r\nHe offered her some practical advice.\r\nWhat are the practical implications of the proposal?\r\nThere are some obvious practical applications of the research.\r\nIn practical terms, it means spending less.', '', '', '2024-01-08 07:17:37', 'view/uploads/image/37_17_14_8_1_2024_image.png', 'view/uploads/audio/37_17_14_8_1_2024_audio.mp3', '', 0),
(120, 'reference', '(noun)', '/ˈrefrəns/', 'a mention of something / tham khảo / tham chiếu', 'Knowing what had happened, I avoided making any reference to (= mentioning) weddings.\r\nShe made no reference to her illness but only to her future plans.\r\nthe President’s passing reference to (= brief mention of) the end of the war\r\nHer book contains many biblical references.\r\nThe emergency nurse can treat minor injuries without reference to a doctor.', '', '', '2024-01-08 07:24:49', 'view/uploads/image/49_24_14_8_1_2024_image.png', 'view/uploads/audio/49_24_14_8_1_2024_audio.mp3', '', 0),
(122, 'cache', '(noun)', '/kæʃ/', 'bộ nhớ đệm / kho lưu trữ', 'An arms cache.\r\nPlacing scripts in external files has some advantages:\r\n1. It separates HTML and code.\r\n2. It makes HTML and JavaScript easier to read and maintain.\r\n3. Cached JavaScript files can speed up page loads.', '', '', '2024-01-08 07:31:25', 'view/uploads/image/59_40_14_21_1_2024_image.png', 'view/uploads/audio/25_31_14_8_1_2024_audio.mp3', '', 0),
