(217, 'so-called', '(adjective)', '/ˌsəʊ ˈkɔːld/', 'used to show that you do not think that the word or phrase that is being used to describe / used to introduce the word that people usually use to describe something', 'Let\'s write alert, which is a so-called JavaScript function.\r\nHow have these so-called improvements helped the local community?\r\nartists from the so-called \'School of London\'', '', '', '2024-01-11 23:34:16', 'view/uploads/image/16_34_6_12_1_2024_image.png', 'view/uploads/audio/16_34_6_12_1_2024_audio.mp3', '', 0),
